Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.36,0:04:25.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and we get this result
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.00,0:04:29.20,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It looks like it's done a nice job writing a description
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.20,0:04:31.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,introducing a stunning mid-century inspired office chair
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,perfect addition, and so on
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.56,0:04:34.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But when I look at this, I go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:36.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,boy, this is really long
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.56,0:04:39.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It's done a nice job doing exactly what I asked it to
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.60,0:04:44.68,灰英字,,0,0,0,,which is start from the technical fact sheet and write a product description
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.68,0:04:46.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But when I look at this, I go
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.76,0:04:50.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,this is long, maybe we want it to be a little bit shorter
