Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:05:02.12,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So I will then clarify my prompt
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.12,0:05:10.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,um, and say, use at most 50 words to try to give
