Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.92,0:05:31.56,灰英字,,0,0,0,,both stylish and practical
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.56,0:05:37.44,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Not bad. Um, and let me double-check the length that this is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.44,0:05:39.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,So I'm going to take the response, split it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.72,0:05:41.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,according to where the space is
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.04,0:05:42.76,灰英字,,0,0,0,,and then, you know, print out the length
