Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.92,0:05:45.00,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It's actually not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.00,0:05:48.60,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Um, large language models are okay
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.60,0:05:53.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,but not that great at following instructions about a very precise word count
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.36,0:05:54.48,灰英字,,0,0,0,,But this is actually not bad
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.48,0:05:58.96,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Sometimes it will print out something with 60 or 65 and so on words
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.96,0:06:01.36,灰英字,,0,0,0,,but it's kind of within reason
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.36,0:06:04.08,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Some of the things you could try to do would be
