Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.20,0:06:32.28,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Um, and then I've also seen people sometimes do things like
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.28,0:06:35.92,灰英字,,0,0,0,,uh, I don't know, use at most 280 characters
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.92,0:06:40.04,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Large language models, because of the way they interpret text
