Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.48,0:06:52.72,灰英字,,0,0,0,,It's actually surprisingly close
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.72,0:06:56.32,灰英字,,0,0,0,,Usually a large language model is- doesn't get it quite this close
